scenes.description: Mori Calliope explores the pool area of a virtual resort and discovers a bar.
Mori Calliope steps behind the bar, interacts with her chat, and experiments with the room's physics by throwing and juggling bottles.
Mori Calliope enters a museum-like hall featuring a statue of YAGOO and tributes to HoloJustice and HoloMyth.
